description.narrative: The program will support the government's key reform priorities aimed at achieving higher and pro-poor economic growth that is sustainable over the medium term. The reform priorities include efforts to improve the investment climate, strengthen public financial management, and governance, and enhance poverty reduction and access to public service delivery.
